ji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"燒山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b418688286b525bedd78b81eedc63ed1b520ad8","tid":1715721,"uid":81716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:49:22.000Z","msg":"中大仲非常有精神領袖既意義，首先唔係大台，係中大仔既存在依家就係俾我地一種反擊既希望，可以話佢地就係站在第一線做對抗<br />\n<br />\n我地士氣係得到無限振奮，本來接近一淡死水既運動再次復活到6，7月咁，全靠中大仔奮勇抗敵，所以中大絕不能讓，絕對不棄守<br />\n<br />\n反之如果今次呢個中大要塞輸在我方落荒而逃，好不容易累積到既士氣會打散哂，再去番10月個時整時間表，到到開花都對不準政權，人們開始厭倦太多抗爭活動，令到運動失敗，好似五年前咁被清算<br />\n<br />\n但只要贏左，就掉番轉得到無堅不催既中大勇武士兵，以及好多好多受影響既民眾，再集合連同公會大三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一股作氣攻上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以中大各大學一戰一定不能輸，不能Be water <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84690480b9f9af3d70b5f333e13e75abf9c3b52c","tid":1715721,"uid":81716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd802d9053e9489383313f5546f2ba303a046f8b","tid":1715721,"uid":37135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"如果開真槍 64咁 走唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:50:53.000Z","msg":"之前西灣河都開左真槍<